&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p id="miGRTl"&gt; In 2024, UMG did not rely on chance, or even ordinary business practices, to “break through the noise” on Spotify, and likely other music platforms. It instead launched a campaign to manipulate and...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
